'''Vera&John''' 是一家总部设在马耳他的网上赌场。 Vera&John 由  Dumarca Gaming Ltd 经营，它的母公司 Dumarca Holdings PLC 于2015年由Intertain Group Ltd 收购。<ref>{{cite web |title = Intertain Group Limited Announces 2014 Third Quarter Financial Results Adjusted EBITDA Up 50% Over Q2 |url = http://media.wix.com/ugd/8b85e7_63b03878e7324f6d816b2f511127ecb0.pdf |publisher = Alberta Securities Commission |accessdate = 2015-07-31 |archive-date = 2016-03-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172104/http://media.wix.com/ugd/8b85e7_63b03878e7324f6d816b2f511127ecb0.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>Intertain Group Ltd 在多伦多证券交易所上市。 Vera&John 由马耳他博彩管理局和英国博彩委员会发牌及监管。<ref>{{cite web |title = DYNAMIC SEAL OF AUTHORISATION |url = https://www.authorisation.mga.org.mt/verification.aspx?lang=en&company=c0e82570-bf83-4ecc-bda3-89ecb92d5b0e |publisher = Malta Gaming Authority |accessdate = 2015-07-31 |archive-date = 2016-03-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160315000352/https://www.authorisation.mga.org.mt/verification.aspx?lang=en&company=c0e82570-bf83-4ecc-bda3-89ecb92d5b0e |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title = The Gambling Commission Reference 39408 |url = https://secure.gamblingcommission.gov.uk/gccustomweb/PublicRegister/PRAccountDetails.aspx?accountNo=39408 |publisher = http://www.gamblingcommission.gov.uk/Home.aspx |accessdate = 2015-07-31 |archive-date = 2020-01-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200107161441/https://secure.gamblingcommission.gov.uk/PublicRegister/home |dead-url = no }}</ref>Vera&John 由 Jörgen Nordlund 创建，他过去曾因为创建 Maria Bingo 而闻名，该公司于2007年被 Unibet 以5400万英镑收购。<ref>{{cite web |title = Unibet’s acquisition of Maria Holdings finalised |url = http://news.cision.com/unibet-group-plc/r/unibet-s-acquisition-of-maria-holdings-finalised,c321804 |publisher = news.cision.com |accessdate = 2015-07-31 |archive-date = 2016-03-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170809/http://news.cision.com/unibet-group-plc/r/unibet-s-acquisition-of-maria-holdings-finalised,c321804 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 简史 ==
*2010 - Vera&John 赌场启动， 主要针对北欧博彩市场， 博彩游戏来自 Betsoft, Microgaming 以及 NYX Gaming。
*2011 - Net Entertainment 游戏被添加到 Vera&John的游戏选择中。
*2013 - 在 Vera&John 赌场中可以玩 Yggdrasil Gaming 的游戏。<ref>{{cite web |title = CHERRY Annual Report 2013 |url = http://en.cherry.se/media/22542/cherry-en-2013_web.pdf |publisher = Cherry AB |page = 9 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303195539/http://en.cherry.se/media/22542/cherry-en-2013_web.pdf |archivedate = 2016-03-03 |accessdate = 2015-07-31 }}</ref>
*2014 - Vera&John 宣称成为第一个接受比特币作为支付选项的规范的网上赌场， 结果却在3个星期后暂停了比特币支付设施。<ref>{{cite web |title = Vera&John becomes first regulated online casino to accept Bitcoin 30 January 2014 |url = http://www.igamingbusiness.com/news/verajohn-becomes-first-regulated-online-casino-accept-bitcoin |publisher = iGaming Business Magazine |accessdate = 2015-07-31 |archive-date = 2015-06-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150627050450/http://www.igamingbusiness.com/news/verajohn-becomes-first-regulated-online-casino-accept-bitcoin |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title = Vera&John suspends Bitcoin payment facility 16 April 2014 |url = http://www.igamingbusiness.com/news/verajohn-suspends-bitcoin-payment-facility |publisher = iGaming Business Magazine |accessdate = 2015-07-31 |archive-date = 2015-06-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150627043416/http://www.igamingbusiness.com/news/verajohn-suspends-bitcoin-payment-facility |dead-url = yes }}</ref>
